transcripts:
[MUSIC PLAYING]

Every coffee bean grinds differently. The Grind Control by Breville is the first coffee maker with an adjustable grinder and calibration so you can customize your exact taste preference. Let's see it in action. Brew any size carafe, cup, or mug without compromising on taste. The Grind Control brought to you by the food thinkers of Breville.
